title: North Melbourne Grand Final Breakfast (Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet - Australian Government) ...
text: ( Source : Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet - Australian Government ) Good morning , and thank you for inviting me to this year's North Melbourne breakfast. What a day - it's hot in the city, excitement, pulsing with anticipation -
